		<title>Mayo Clinic study finds remote monitoring may detect early complications, reduce burden for lung transplant patients</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-study-finds-remote-monitoring-may-detect-early-complications-reduce-burden-for-lung-transplant-patients/
		
