		<title>Mayo Clinic Q&amp;A: What is life like after an organ transplant or donation?</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-what-is-life-like-after-an-organ-transplant-or-donation/
		
